 methods for teaching and learning based on the interconnectedness of life, Taoism, Teaching, and Learning develops an inspiring vision for education and helps us to see our world in a deeply holistic and meaningful way.  afunded by University of Toronto Libraries  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aEDUCATION / Teaching Methods & Materials / General.2bisacsh  aLao-Tzu.  aMontessori.  aTaoist teaching and learning.  acompassionate teaching.  acontemplative education.  aeducation.  aholistic education.  akindergarten.  amindfulness.  anature based learning.  aspirituality.  ateaching methods.1 aLi, Xiang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLin, Jing, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuan, Tian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb2 aUniversity of Toronto Librariesefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Comm 2022 Englishz978311099395008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Communication 2022z9783110994186oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076715540uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/9781487551568zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487551568zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps